Francis de Wolff https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Francis_de_Wolff 0 Francis de Wolff (7 January 1913 – 18 April 1984) was an English character actor. Large, bearded, and beetle-browed, he was often cast as villains in both film and television. Francis_de_Wolff ( 7_January_1913 – 18_April_1984 ) was an_English_character_actor .
